but if I show up back to work

17:59.426 --> 18:02.255
completely hammered,
there's gonna be hell to pay.

18:02.298 --> 18:04.257
I got you covered.

18:04.300 --> 18:06.346
I'll put in a word
with the big guy.

18:06.389 --> 18:07.521
With Pierce?

18:07.564 --> 18:09.305
No, think bigger.

18:09.349 --> 18:10.480
The commissioner?

18:10.524 --> 18:15.703
It's an anadrome for D-O-G.

18:15.746 --> 18:18.488
[laughing]:
I love how weird you are.

18:18.532 --> 18:20.011
But I should go.

18:20.055 --> 18:23.232
Or, you could duck
into that closet,

18:23.276 --> 18:25.147
take off all your clothes.

18:25.191 --> 18:26.844
I'll go freshen up.

18:26.888 --> 18:28.542
Meet you in there.

18:28.585 --> 18:31.153
Then, do the same.

18:31.197 --> 18:33.503
That's really not a good idea.

