18:58.572 --> 19:00.922
If I could just, um...

19:00.965 --> 19:02.358
[badge clatters]

19:02.402 --> 19:04.404
Right there.

19:08.712 --> 19:10.366
I don't understand.
Why is it taking so long

19:10.410 --> 19:12.542
to find Kevin Winstead's
drug contacts

19:12.586 --> 19:14.109
on your computer thingy?

19:14.153 --> 19:16.067
It's easier said
than done, Lucifer.

19:16.111 --> 19:17.373
Well, the man is a degenerate.

19:17.417 --> 19:20.333
He must have been arrested
a thousand times.

19:20.376 --> 19:21.421
Rich families
like the Winsteads,

19:21.464 --> 19:22.944
they're all about appearances.

19:22.987 --> 19:24.511
And they've been covering
Kevin's run-ins with the law

19:24.554 --> 19:25.729
since he was a teenager.

19:25.773 --> 19:28.558
Look, getting a hit,
it might take some time.

19:28.602 --> 19:30.908
So why don't you go home,
get some sleep and...

19:30.952 --> 19:32.693
[quietly]:
Look, I can't.

19:32.736 --> 19:33.998
[whispers]:
Why?

19:34.042 --> 19:36.262
Because if I am
this Angel of San Bernardino,

19:36.305 --> 19:38.568
and I go to sleep,
then I might do it again.

19:38.612 --> 19:39.961
Okay, well,
just don't sleep then.

19:40.004 --> 19:41.223
Hold on.

19:41.267 --> 19:43.182
That is an excellent plan,
Detective.

19:43.225 --> 19:44.922
I'll just never sleep again.

