21:50.570 --> 21:52.180
Booth?

21:52.223 --> 21:53.877
Yes, the FBI agent on Bones.

21:53.921 --> 21:55.705
The TV show?
Uh-huh.

21:55.749 --> 21:58.273
Watched all 12 seasons.
It's riveting stuff.

21:58.317 --> 21:59.883
It's like watching
a documentary of us.

