No coccyx.

22:20.164 --> 22:23.864
What I did find
was surveillance video

22:23.907 --> 22:26.823
of Kevin getting arrested
for possession a few months ago.

22:26.867 --> 22:28.303
Oh, goody.
[sniffs]

22:28.347 --> 22:29.870
Okay.
Mm-hmm.

22:29.913 --> 22:31.437
So who's his doltish

22:31.480 --> 22:32.568
sparring partner?
Uh,

22:32.612 --> 22:34.396
Matt Kessman,
